cript-core-32-object-json\u002F","Lb9tAs1eSPzTmi5A1Dx54Pw9PeGtvB1ULD-GWEpLq8E",{"newer":718,"older":722},{"url":719,"title":720,"date":721},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2020\u002F11\u002F13\u002Fjavascript-core-33-object-chapter-quiz\u002F","JavaScript Core Concepts (33): Object — Chapter Wrap-up Quiz","2020-11-13 21:32:44",{"url":723,"title":724,"date":725},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2020\u002F11\u002F11\u002Fpixijs-v5-tutorial-40-finale\u002F","PixiJS V5 Tutorial (40) - The Finale: A Year-Long Marathon Wraps Up","2020-11-11 09:09:43",[727,732,737],{"url":728,"title":729,"date":730,"readingMinutes":731},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2026\u002F03\u002F10\u002Fweb-crypto-api-encryption-guide\u002F","No crypto Package, No Node.js — The Web Crypto API Does It All in the Browser","2026-03-10 09:45:08","9",{"url":733,"title":734,"date":735,"readingMinutes":736},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F08\u002Fjquery-why-it-declined\u002F","jQuery Was Once King — So Why Did It Fall Off?","2025-12-08 21:35:24","7",{"url":738,"title":739,"date":740,"readingMinutes":286},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2025\u002F12\u002F05\u002Fjavascript-generator-functions\u002F","What Are JavaScript Generator Functions (function*)? The Function You Can Pause and Resume","2025-12-05 13:40:31",1784020360116]